name: Thought Bubble Pre-Commission, Bust
description: Only order if you will be at Thought Bubble Comic Con, November 23 - 24, 2013. Busts are drawn on 9x12" Bristol board with pen, India ink and optional Copic or ink wash toning at my discretion (you may also specify if you would prefer no toning). While ordering your commission, please indicate which character you'd like, and you can pick up your finished piece at the show! Email me at mingdoyle @ gmail.com with any questions. Thank you!
